<TEXT>
<P>
NAIROBI, April 15 (Xinhua) -- Kenyan President Daniel arap Moi
left here today for Arusha, northern Tanzania, to attend the
Fourth Great Lakes Regional Summit on Burundi.
</P>
<P>
