Sanctions Committee meeting and a Ministerial Technical Committee
meeting.
</P>
<P>
Julius Nyerere, mediator for the Burundi crisis and former
Tanzanian President, is scheduled to submit a report to the
summit on the progress of economic sanctions imposed on
Burundi since last July.
