<HEADLINE> Spanish Bank to Invest in Zanzibar </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
DAR ES SALAAM, April 15 (Xinhua) -- A Spanish Bank, Banco
Bilbao Vizca (BBVT) has signed an agreement with the Zanzibar
