they would take off.
</P>
<P>
The Finance Minister, Amina Salim Ali, who signed the
agreement on behalf of the government, pledged government's
assistance towards establishment of the projects.
</P>
<P>
Zanzibar adopted the investment Act in 1986 with the purpose
of rehabilitating its ailing economy which experienced
difficullties following the collapse of clove market in the
world. 
