colleagues, to let them know the position of the service today, and
rub minds on how to positively move forward," Abubakar said.
</P>
<P>
He admitted that the air force is not at its best level of
operational capability.
</P>
<P>
An embargo of weapons and spare parts were imposed on Nigeria by
West nations after Nigeria hanged Saro-Wiwa and eight other Ogoni
activists in November 1995.  
