been rescued if authorities had worked together, says the special
report.
</P>
<P>
The commission calls for in a report a complete overhaul of the
country's policing system.
</P>
<P>
The scandal broke eight months ago in Belgium with discovery of
four bodies of murdered girls. A fifth victim was found last
month.
</P>
<P>
The cases deeply shocked the country, provoking an
unprecedented crisis of popular confidence in governing
institutions.  
