front's Steering Committee here tomorrow, a key committee member
said today.
</P>
<P>
G.K. Moopanar, who himself is the leading candidate for new UF
leader, told reporters in Chennai, capital of Tamil Nadu state,
that the leadership question would be resolved amicably, according
to the Press Trust of India.
