the UF parliamentary party, has offered to step down after losing
a vote of confidence in his government, paving the way for the
election of a new UF leader.
</P>
<P>
The change of leadership in the UF is a precondition for the
Congress party to renew support for the front to form a new
government. The Congress party withdrew its support for the UF
late last month.  
