results. Their productivity was increased, making Tanzania's
potentials more attractive to foreign investors, he noted.
</P>
<P>
Naiko said plans were underway to enact a law which will lead
to creation of an investment authority.
</P>
<P>
"The new IPC will be the body responsible for dealing directly
with the established bureaucracy on behalf of the investors" in
terms of acquiring land, getting permits, obtaining licenses and
residence permits, he said.
