financing for infrastructure projects worth 2.2 billion U.S.
dollars under the country's build-operate-transfer (BOT) scheme.
</P>
<P>
The team, led by Trade and Industry Secretary Cesar Bautista,
will stage investment roadshows in Paris, London and other two
European cities on April 17-23, according to today's local press
reports.
</P>
<P>
