at least 20 billion dollars to improve its infrastructure to
sustain current economic growth momentum.
</P>
<P>
The estimated massive infrastructure financial needs apparently
exceed the government's financing capability and need financing
from private sector.
</P>
<P>
To attract private investment, the government launched the BOT
scheme years ago, under which foreign investors can build an
infrastructure facility, operate it for years and then transfer it
to the government. 
